Class DefaultJob<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.felix.ipojo.extender.internal.DefaultJob<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Callable<T>, Job<T>

    public abstract class DefaultJob<T>
extends Object
implements Job<T>
    A callable object implementing Bundle Reference. It makes the Bundle object accessible by the processing job. This class is intended to be extended.
